I"<h2 id="nice-to-meet-you">Nice to meet you!</h2>

<p>I am a physician and epidemiologist working in the Department of International health
at <a href="https://www.maastrichtuniversity.nl/">Maastricht University</a>.</p>

<p>I am also a PhD student in health demography at <a href="https://www.imprs-phds.mpg.de/">IMPRS-PHDS</a>, advised by Helmut Brand, Fanny Janssen and Tobias Vogt. My PhD is focused on structural determinants of mortality convergence in the European Union, particularly social and economic policy.</p>
